text: WKOT-LP (102.1 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Wimauma, Florida. The station is owned by New Beginning Baptist Temple. It airs a religious format. The station was assigned the WKOT-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on April 5, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * KOT-LP KOT-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Florida Category:Religious radio stations in the United States Category:Hillsborough County, Florida KOT- LP
